  {{else}}
    <p>
      <em>You can now apply for grants to help with the impact of the coronavirus (COVID-19) on your organisation through your Local Authority. If you haven’t already, we would advise that you look into the options available from your Local Authority before applying to the TSRF. You can find information about these as well as contact details by following this link:</em>
