  {{else}}
  <p>
    We are sorry but the TRSF is not the right fund for you. This fund is to help charities and organisations to stabilise cashflow issues during this difficult period. You may be eligible for other funding, <a href="/support/coronavirus/funding">find out more about other COVID-19 emergency funds</a>.
  </p>
  {{/if ~}}
  {{else}}
  <p>
    We are sorry but the TRSF is not the right fund for you. This is an emergency fund to support organisations that would otherwise be in a stable financial position, but that find themselves now badly affected financially due to the outbreak. You may be eligible for other funding, <a href="/support/coronavirus/funding">find out more about other COVID-19 emergency funds</a>.
  </p>
  {{/if ~}}
  {{else}}
  <p>
    We are sorry but the TSRF is not the right fund for you. This fund aims to help charities and social enterprises delivering services prior to the COVID-19 outbreak. You may be eligible for other funding, <a href="/support/coronavirus/funding">find out more about other COVID-19 emergency funds</a>
  </p>
  {{/if ~}}
  {{else}}
  <p>
    We are sorry but the TSRF is not the right fund for you. This fund is for registered charities, voluntary organisations and social enterprises only. You may be eligible for other funding, <a href="/support/coronavirus/funding">find out more about other COVID-19 emergency funds</a>.
